You were supposed to have this row
and we were supposed to have this row.

00:25:15.647 --> 00:25:17.983 line:95%,end
Well, until I see a plate
on the back of this chair

00:25:18.049 --> 00:25:20.352 line:95%,end
with your name on it that you bought it,
I'm not moving.

00:25:21.253 --> 00:25:24.189 line:95%,end
CHLOE: <i>I guess I'm having</i>
<i>more confidence in myself,</i>

00:25:24.256 --> 00:25:27.926 line:95%,end
<i>because backstage</i>
<i>I'm not as nervous anymore.</i>

00:25:27.993 --> 00:25:29.494 line:5%,start
My nerves are more settled.

00:25:29.561 --> 00:25:33.398 line:5%,start
I just go over the dance
and kind of have fun.

00:25:33.465 --> 00:25:36.268 line:95%,end
This week,
I think I'm going to be (indistinct)

