00:25:38.136 --> 00:25:39.237 line:95%,end
<i>with "Don't Touch Me."</i>

00:25:39.304 --> 00:25:42.607 line:95%,end
(crowd cheering)

00:25:42.674 --> 00:25:45.577 line:95%,end
CHRISTI: <i>Today Chloe and Maddie</i>
