00:25:45.644 --> 00:25:48.313 line:95%,end
<i>And I think Chloe is actually</i>
<i>holding up really well today.</i>

00:25:48.380 --> 00:25:50.582 line:95%,end
<i>I don't see any signs of nerves.</i>

